data.description: This charming and stately brick home located near the heart of Goldsboro features 4 bedrooms and 3 baths with an additional flex space for office, school room or bedroom. It also boasts a new master suite addition which includes 2 walk-in closets, a spa like bath which includes walk-in shower and a separate tub all complete with custom tile work and marble tops. This home has beautiful and original hardwood floors throughout, original hand made trim, and updated double pane vinyl windows that allow plenty of natural light. In the kitchen you will find beautiful custom hand made wooden cabinets with Ubatuba Granite countertops. Enjoy time in your family room with gas fireplace or head out to your spacious sunroom with original slate floors. Walk outside to your fenced in back yard complete with patio and outdoor fireplace. This home has many storage options including, multiple closets in the 2 car garage and throughout home, multiple shelves in laundry room and a floored attic space upstairs. Other unique and important features include an 8x12 storage barn, well fed in ground sprinkler system, updated electric panel in 2009,  duct work and foam insulation in crawl space and attic added in 2010, new roof for main home in 2013 and new 1st floor roof shingle/metal in 2022. A ring alarm system can also convey.
